1. *Pozdravite* svoje roditelje od mene. (Say hello to your parents from me.)
2. *Pozdravite* gospodina Markovića kad ga vidite. (Say hello to Mr. Markovic when you see him.)
3. Želela bih da vas *pozdravim* u ime celog tima. (I would like to greet you on behalf of the whole team.)
4. Molim vas da *pozdravite* direktora kad ga sretnete. (Please greet the director when you meet him.)
5. Svi smo *pozdravili* novog zaposlenog na sastanku. (We all greeted the new employee at the meeting.)
6. Kolege iz inostranstva poslale su nam *pozdrave* i želele su nam uspeh u poslu. (Colleagues from abroad sent us greetings and wished us success in our work.)
7. Bila sam jako srećna kad sam čula da si me *pozdravio* u svojoj knjizi. (I was very happy when I heard that you greeted me in your book.)
8. Nismo stigli da se *pozdravimo* pre nego što si otišao. (We didn't have time to say goodbye before you left.)
9. Ako vam treba nešto od mene, *pozdravite* me. (If you need anything from me, greet me.)
10. Uputio je *pozdrav* publici i zahvalio se na pozivu. (He sent greetings to the audience and thanked them for the invitation.)